cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting and tracking human poses in videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel architecture for encoding and predicting spatio-temporal affinity fields, which involves deep learning techniques and could fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of PoseTrack benchmarks, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) applications.
